### Mise à jour utilisateur (nécessite AUTH - voir section tests protection)
# PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/users/f5f503b4-5861-4149-b868-5c9597415757
# Content-Type: application/json
# Cookie: accessToken=VOTRE_TOKEN_ICI
#
# {
#   "username": "JesuisAdminMec",
#   "email": "admin@admin.com",
#   "avatar_url": "https://admin.com/grand-admin.png",
#   "password": "Jesuis.membre1"
# }

### Delete ONE User (nécessite ADMIN - voir section tests protection)
# DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/users/3a9f3244-c29c-4b25-b2ed-3ecf5dae5c21
### Mise à jour multiple de plusieurs champs d'un utilisateur
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/users/f5f503b4-5861-4149-b868-5c9597415757
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "JesuisAdminMec",
  "email": "admin@admin.com",
  "avatar_url": "https://admin.com/grand-admin.png",
  "password": "Jesuis.membre1",
  "confirmPassword": "Jesuis.membre1"
}

### Delete ONE User
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/users/445bfd95-1c81-48db-8844-71dee02989b1

