GET http://localhost:4000/api/matches/551996

### Create Match (NÉCESSITE NULL API_ID DANS LA DB)(nécessite ADMIN)
# POST http://localhost:4000/api/matches
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJiOTUzYTM0Yi0xZTZhLTQ5ZmQtYmFjYi01YzBjMjU2NGM4N2EiLCJ1c2VyUm9sZSI6IkFETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY5MjAyNjc0LCJleHAiOjE3NjkyMDYyNzR9.lespq0SwuQkNOdwPVHz6L7T89K2w-RGUkIKiUM8mfIE

{
  "api_id": "999999",
  "home_team": "Test FC",
  "away_team": "Test United",
  "competition_id": "2021",
  "match_date": "2025-06-01T20:00:00Z",
  "status": "SCHEDULED"
}

### Update Match (NÉCESSITE NULL API_ID DANS LA DB)(nécessite ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/matches/MATCH_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: accessToken=VOTRE_TOKEN_ADMIN_ICI

{
  "status": "FINISHED",
  "home_score": 2,
  "away_score": 1
}

### Delete Match (nécessite ADMIN)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/matches/MATCH_ID
Cookie: accessToken=VOTRE_TOKEN_ADMIN_ICI

