### TESTS PROTECTION ROUTES (Middleware Role)

### GET /api/users/:username - PUBLIC (pas de token nécessaire)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users/user_9

### GET /api/users - Sans auth (401) | MEMBER (403) | ADMIN (200)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users
Cookie: accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI4MmU0YmNjMC1mZGRhLTRiYmItYjczOS01ZjQwNzk5ZDVkODciLCJ1c2VyUm9sZSI6IkFETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY5MDAxNDE5LCJleHAiOjE3NjkwMDUwMTl9.aBAD6R-2sV9OwysGa9plexM9Dz9sIRUf8l-ZAcdiar4

### PATCH /api/users/:id - Sans auth (401) | Modifier autre (403) | Modifier soi/ADMIN (200)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/users/00000000-1000-4000-9000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI4MmU0YmNjMC1mZGRhLTRiYmItYjczOS01ZjQwNzk5ZDVkODciLCJ1c2VyUm9sZSI6IkFETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY5MDAxNDE5LCJleHAiOjE3NjkwMDUwMTl9.aBAD6R-2sV9OwysGa9plexM9Dz9sIRUf8l-ZAcdiar4

{
  "username": "TestModification"
}

### DELETE /api/users/:id - Sans auth (401) | MEMBER (403) | ADMIN (200)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/users/00000000-1000-4000-9000-000000000001
Cookie: accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI4MmU0YmNjMC1mZGRhLTRiYmItYjczOS01ZjQwNzk5ZDVkODciLCJ1c2VyUm9sZSI6IkFETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY5MDAxNDE5LCJleHAiOjE3NjkwMDUwMTl9.aBAD6R-2sV9OwysGa9plexM9Dz9sIRUf8l-ZAcdiar4

### GET /api/predictions - Sans auth (401) | MEMBER (403) | ADMIN (200)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/predictions
Cookie: accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI4MmU0YmNjMC1mZGRhLTRiYmItYjczOS01ZjQwNzk5ZDVkODciLCJ1c2VyUm9sZSI6IkFETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY5MDAxNDE5LCJleHAiOjE3NjkwMDUwMTl9.aBAD6R-2sV9OwysGa9plexM9Dz9sIRUf8l-ZAcdiar4

